description: This stunning 3BD/2.5BA townhouse features a private roof deck and garage parking! The first level offers direct garage access, a bedroom with a custom Murphy bed, and private patio. The second floor boasts a beautiful kitchen with custom cabinetry, large island, Viking stainless steel appliances, and quartz countertops. The bright living room includes a gas fireplace, designated dining area, and a half bath. On the top level, the primary bedroom offers an ensuite bath and two custom closets, plus a second bedroom, full bath with a frameless step-in glass shower and laundry complete this floor. Access the roof deck via a skylight with hydraulic lift, featuring gas, water, electricity, and a speaker system with stunning city views. Additional features include private basement storage, hardwood floors, and proximity to South Boston’s best restaurants and shops. This is the one!
